
:author: Koichi Takahashi


Prerequisites
-------------------------

1. autotools
   (autoconf, automake, libtool)
2. GNU Scientific Library (GSL).
3. Python 2.4 or later.
4. Scipy 0.5 or later, Numpy 1.0 or later.
5. CppUnit

If you use Fedora or RedHat line of linux, you may check
if the following RPM packages are installed:

gsl, gsl-devel, numpy, scipy, cppunit, cppunit-devel.


Building this package
-------------------------

1. ./autogen.sh (optional)
2. ./configure
3. make
4. make check (optional)


Testing
-------------------------

% python dimer.py


